  "prompt": "Where is the Royal Enfield Service Center in Kota City?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge up to October 2023, Royal Enfield has authorized service centers in Kota, Rajasthan, operated by official dealers. To find the most accurate and up-to-date information on Royal Enfield service centers in Kota, you can use the following methods:\n\n### 1. **Official Royal Enfield Dealer Locator**\nVisit the [Royal Enfield Dealer Locator](https://www.royalenfield.com/in/en/dealer-locator/) on their official website. Here's how you can use it:\n- **Step 1:** Go to the [Dealer Locator](https://www.royalenfield.com/in/en/dealer-locator/) page.\n- **Step 2:** Enter \"Kota\" in the search bar or allow the website to access your location.\n- **Step 3:** The tool will display a list of authorized dealerships and service centers in Kota along with their addresses, contact numbers, and operating hours.\n\n### 2. **Contacting Royal Enfield Customer Support**\nYou can reach out directly to Royal Enfield's customer support for assistance:\n- **Phone:** [Insert official contact number, e.g., 1800-XXX-XXXX]\n- **Email:** [Insert official customer support email, e.g., support@royalenfield.com]\n\n### 3. **Popular Authorized Dealers in Kota**\nWhile it's always best to verify with the official dealer locator, some known authorized Royal Enfield dealers in Kota include:\n\n- **HM Motors**\n  - **Address:** [Insert complete address if available]\n  - **Contact:** [Insert contact number]\n\n- **Kota Royal Enfield**\n  - **Address:** [Insert complete address if available]\n  - **Contact:** [Insert contact number]\n\n*(Please verify these details through the official dealer locator or by contacting Royal Enfield directly, as dealership information can change.)*\n\n### 4. **Visiting Local Showrooms**\nIf you prefer in-person assistance, visiting a local Royal Enfield showroom in Kota can provide you with immediate information regarding service centers, maintenance schedules, and any ongoing promotions or services.\n\n---\n\n**Note:** It's always recommended to verify the service center details through the official Royal Enfield channels to ensure you receive accurate and up-to-date information.",
